'''艾莉西亞·席薇史東'''（{{lang-en|Alicia Silverstone}}，{{IPAc-en|icon|ə|ˈ|l|iː|s|i|ə|_|ˈ|s|ɪ|l|v|ər|s|t|oʊ|n}}，{{bd|1976年|10月4日|catIdx=Silverstone, Alicia}}）<ref name=biography.com>{{cite web|url=https://www.biography.com/people/alicia-silverstone-240974|title=Alicia Silverstone: Animal Rights Activist, Film Actor/Film Actress, Actress, Film Actress, Activist (1976–)|publisher=[[Biography.com|Biography.com]] ([[FYI_(TV_network)|FYI]] / [[A&E_Networks|A&E Networks]])|access-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227153618/https://www.biography.com/people/alicia-silverstone-240974|archive-date=2018-02-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>是一位美國女演員、作家及模特兒<ref>{{cite book|last=Morgan|first=Adam|title=Eating the Big Fish: How Challenger Brands Can Compete Against Brand Leaders|url=https://archive.org/details/eatingbigfishhow00morg_043|year=2009|publisher=Wiley|isbn=978-0470238271|page=[https://archive.org/details/eatingbigfishhow00morg_043/page/n169 144]}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Vaughn|first=Jacqueline|title=Environmental Activism: A Reference Handbook|year=2003|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-1576079010|page=[https://archive.org/details/environmentalact00swit/page/167 167]|url=https://archive.org/details/environmentalact00swit/page/167}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Photography By Rodale Images |url=https://www.womenshealthmag.com/life/alicia-silverstone-book |title=Alicia Silverstone: The Kind Diet | Women's Health Magazine |publisher=Womenshealthmag.com |date=2012-04-05 |access-date=2012-04-11}}</ref>，知名於電影《[[獨領風騷|獨領風騷]]》（1995年）以及《[[蝙蝠俠與羅賓_(電影)|蝙蝠俠4：急凍人]]》（1997年）的精湛演出。曾在[[史密斯飛船|史密斯飛船]]樂團歌曲〈{{le|Cryin'|Cryin'}}〉MV中演出。

2003年憑藉[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]短命電視劇《{{le|俏紅娘 (電視劇)|Miss Match|俏紅娘}}》入圍[[金球奖音乐及喜剧类剧集最佳女主角|金球奖音乐及喜剧类剧集最佳女主角]]。

